title: Alice in Wonderland (Dub)
alternative_title: Fushigi no Kuni no Alice, Fushigi no Kuni no Alice, Fushigi no Kuni no Alice
description: A retelling of Lewis Carroll's classic tale of the young girl Alice, who follows a white rabbit into a hole, only to find herself in Wonderland, where she meets many interesting characters, both the mysterious Cheshire Cat and the terrible Queen of Hearts.
